compiz-fusion: compiz (Compiz-Fusion OpenGL Window Manager)
compiz-fusion:
compiz-fusion: Compiz-fusion is a compositing window manager that uses 3D graphics 
compiz-fusion: acceleration via OpenGL. It provides various new graphical effects 
compiz-fusion: and features on any desktop environment, including GNOME. It is the 
compiz-fusion: result of the re-unification of the Beryl-project and the community 
compiz-fusion: around the Compiz Window Manager. It seeks to provide an easy and 
compiz-fusion: fun-to-use windowing environment, allowing use of the graphics 
compiz-fusion: hardware to provide impressive effects, amazing speed and unrivalled 
compiz-fusion: usefulness.
